manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Color Assortment Denim isn't just for pants or jackets these days, American Tourister designed the Belle Voyage collection with the world's passion for denim in mind! Both the rich, deep blue denim and the floral indigo sand designs are offset by elegant rose gold components on each piece that include the American Tourister stacked logo plate, zipper pulls and the beveled push button locking handles. Blue Denim Black Red American Tourister Belle Voyage What's So Fashionable About Belle Voyage? Pack your favorite items in one of our most fashionable collections. Fashion meets fun, function and affordability with the Belle Voyage luggage collection from American Tourister. This jazzy collection will have you ready to roll along on your journey in style. Large interior packing compartment Blouse pocket on door panel Shoe pockets on the door panel Interior modesty pocket

Features Gold Accents Gold accents on the logo, zipper pulls and push button locking handle. Integrated top, side and bottom carry handles for easy lifting. 1.5" Expansion Cases expand for added packing capacity. Large front panel interior pocket for added packing organization. Deep main compartment with mesh modesty pocket for personal items. Compression straps keep clothing neatly packed while traveling. Single Airflow Spinner Wheels Smooth-rolling, 'airflow' multi-directional spinner wheels for easy movement. Rolls upright so there is no weight on your arm or shoulder.

About American Tourister At American Tourister, we believe travel should be fun. We take pride in making stylish, high quality, and yeah, fun luggage that you can rely on. Now, over 75 years later, American Tourister is positioned as one of the largest luggage brands in the world. Thanks to its continued tradition of quality and design at a great value, American Tourister is the smart choice for you and your family, offering a wide selection of travel products including luggage items as well as casual, and business bags. We understand how you travel, so we're ready to go when you are with the gear that's right for you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this suitcase
reviews.reviewText: After looking all over at suitcases I chose this one. I had a hard sided 4 wheel case that I spent a lot of money on only to have the airline destroy beyond repair so I knew I only wanted a soft sided 4 wheeler. First off I love that there is one deep inside area as opposed to compartments on two sides. This seems like it is much more efficient with my packing cubes. It has two very deep zipper pockets on the outside perfect for holding all your electronics and necessary travel items. The zippers seem very sturdy as does the suitcase. I chose the red, not because I love the color, but because it cost less than the black. I was pleasantly surprised by the color. It is a lovely shade of cranberry with gold zippers & pulls and I really like the purse like straps on top they should make lifting into the overhead much easier. I'm excited to try it out in a few weeks on my annual girls trip. UPDATE: just returned from a trip and I loved it. Held so much and the handles on side, bottom & top made it so easy to put in overhead bins. So glad I purchased this suitcase ❤️

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sleek and Efficient Travel Companion!
reviews.reviewText: The American Tourister Belle Voyage Softside Luggage is a traveler's dream. Not only does its 21-inch size fit most carry-on restrictions, making domestic travel a breeze, but its design ensures you travel in style. The luggage's smooth, multi-directional 'airflow' spinner wheels ensure hassle-free movement through any terminal. I'm particularly charmed by the elegant rose gold details on the zipper pulls, logo, and handle. The added expandability feature is perfect for those inevitable travel shopping sprees. Plus, with a longer warranty time, this bag promises durability. An absolute gem for every journey!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to maneuver
reviews.reviewText: I don't travel a lot so I didn't want to spend hundreds of dollars on a suitcase. This one is a reasonable price, lightweight, easy to maneuver, a good size, attractive, and perfect for the occasional traveler. The gold zippers make it easy to spot at baggage claim among all the black suitcases.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Gorgeous, but I don't think it is unused.
reviews.reviewText: The first one I received was mis-sewn. This one the wheels have minor tread damage and signs of use. I am keeping it but am a little bit bummed. The color is gorgeous though. I love the sturdy gold zippers and I do like that it is a deep case which will work well with packing cubes. Caution, it may not meet AA, Delta and US Air carry on requirements as they now have a strict 22" maximum and this case is almost an inch over that. The discount carriers still take up to 24" but our family does not use typically use those airlines.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great roller bag!
reviews.reviewText: Bought this bag to travel multiple places in a one month time period! We are now in our fourth destination and it has served me very well! Kauai, Boise, San Diego and now Cape Cod. Holds quite a lot of clothing and expands to fit even more! I never travel without a checked bag, but this piece of luggage allowed me to this time. And boy am I glad! Two of our flights got cancelled or had long delays, requiring us to change flights. It made me so happy to have this carry on with me, not checked! A lifesaver! It seems well made, sturdy and rolls really nicely through hotels and airports. I would definitely recommend! I bought the red 21” bag. Love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great carryon! Looks good and great quality
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I am loving this new travel bag I got. It’s already been on 5 different trips and it still looks brand new. The quality is amazing. It travels easy! The wheels move around and it’s durable! Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this suitcase
reviews.reviewText: I took it on two trips and checked it. It held up nicely. It’s so pretty and roomy enough for several days worth of clothes and shoes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great For Carryon and Walking thru the airport
reviews.reviewText: By the time I realized the wheels on my carry on were broken I didn't have time to get a new one. So I carried two heavy tote bags through the airport to my destination. As soon as I arrived, I went on Amazon to find a carryon that would be delivered before I left to return home - which was about 36 hours. Thank you Amazon. I knew I didn't have to look anywhere else. I read the reviews which helped tremendously. I didn't realize that some had only 2 wheels - so I searched for 4 wheels. This is a great carry on - lightweight and so easy to maneuver in the airport. I was alone with a heavy tote bag. Pulling it on the wheels or walking with it standing up straight was so comfortable. There is plenty of room including the outside pockets. The cranberry color is fun as I always get black! I love it and have no complaints - high recommend!
Precio justo por una maleta que aparenta ser de una mejor gama.

I bought this after carefully looking at the carry on dimensions of the major airlines I fly, and at 21" this was going to fit the bill. This suitcase actually measures 23" tall and 10" deep and didn't fit into the carry on sizer at the airport, so I was required to check it. Super annoying!It's otherwise a nice suitcase, though the carrying handles at the top have to be snapped together and they get in the way of the telescoping handle.

Love my new luggage. Was looking for a 4 wheel for better mobility and it delivered. Holds a more than decent amount and has various compartments. Looks sleek and had little details that were very functional. However, the wheels make it taller and it looks a lot bulkier. Measurements for carry-on might be a little off. This makes it more likely not to fit in the carry-on size check that they have when boarding. Had to pay to get it checked on one of my flights. Other flights were full and offered to check it for free since "it was a big carry-on".

I was able to fit all my close (16 day trip) in this suitcase and there are two compartments for shoes. The one issue I have is that the pull handle will drop as you are walking. It’s really annoying. It might just be an issue with mine.
I love anything denim, so when looking for new luggage, this was perfect. Added bonus that it was a reputable company. Now I have the whole set
